Congratulations! You have a Joomla site! Joomla makes it easy to build a website just the way you want it and keep it simple to update and maintain.

'core_content_id': Joomla is a flexible and powerful platform
'core_type_alias': whether you are building a small site for yourself or a huge site with hundreds of thousands of visitors. Joomla is open source
'core_title': which means you can make it work just the way you want it to.

The content in this installation of Joomla has been designed to give you an in depth tour of Joomla''s features.
